sequence locks for reading/writing
epoch for when to delete nodes in batches (dont delete inline)
versioning for repeatable read
leave deleted nodes in the list until a background thread purges them
every info needs a transaction id so we know when to get rid of it and which one to use for a read
put a fast spin lock in every node for write-write situations
use head dummy node at max height
use pread to read the data for a row
gold-standard signal-and-condition-variable sleep loop
allocate big chunks of memory with malloc and placement new the nodes/values on them
values/nodes/keys may have to be ref counted
secondary index K needs to be composite key (some type that includes the primary K)
